                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined. Q.</hi> How long after the prisoner and Pulley were married did you see them together? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> When they married he took a shop at Leighton-Buzzard, and I lived with them about a fort<lb></lb>night.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
